{"tid":2276390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家食肉會唔會聯想到隻動物？","createTime":"2020-11-07T20:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T07:05:32.000Z","uid":220382,"like":26,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"8e39c78dae7e39b206a46d50a8c78c3d3609aafb","tid":2276390,"uid":220382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:09:13.000Z","msg":"純討論<br />\n大家食肉有無諗過其實係動物分肢？<br />\n隻動物要養要長大要死 斬頭斬手斬腳<br />\n先有魚頭 豬手豬腳<br />\n因為有素食 食肉又唔係必須<br />\n又有無人諗過同d人食貓狗無咩分別<br />\n即係塊豬扒其實係生勾勾識fing尾既豬<br />\n隻燒乳鴿曾經係隻唱歌既鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹某日諗過下 分享下討論下"},{"pid":"46441acab0b166d47cb3dfd8d370fa24b6989447","tid":2276390,"uid":96708,"like":35,"dislike":8,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:13:59.000Z","msg":"食魚生最新鮮就係你面前切，正呀<br />\n<br />\nbtw我養雀都食乳鴿個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77348060a9d19032fd3fde4307150431d0b302e","tid":2276390,"uid":96708,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:15:53.000Z","msg":"澳洲直頭合法打獵袋鼠，因為太撚多影響生態平衡，射殺完就加餸，新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e221dd6a1e01a68a4c9314697893a5268aec631","tid":2276390,"uid":212336,"like":68,"dislike":5,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:16:46.000Z","msg":"咁你又無諗過啲菜比人連根拔起又幾痛?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食物鏈本來就環環相扣，咁先係自然"},{"pid":"0c9642756fc2ab6bbad18e7d33f927e01211d781","tid":2276390,"uid":288455,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:21:09.000Z","msg":"人類係雜食動物，食肉係必須，你試吓食素唔食supplements 睇吓捱到幾耐？如果可以食素唔食supplements 又生存到嘅話先至好講食肉唔係必須"},{"pid":"5fd94435ae5ad552e7c8ea04469da8639bca16b4","tid":2276390,"uid":135284,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"食物鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食素先係破壞生態平衡囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a722d26cd06452c84fd79430eff028a2eddf091","tid":2276390,"uid":55390,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:24:21.000Z","msg":"有 但係肉個種鮮味食素完全代替唔到所以都係戒唔到<br />\n不過會傾向唔浪費食物同支持人道飼養/屠宰<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n早排港台有個節目講過呢個問題 分別送唔同家畜俾啲家庭養兩個禮拜睇下會唔會影響佢地食肉嘅選擇 結果大部分都放棄唔到食肉 不過會支持啲人道啲嘅animal product"},{"pid":"a2aea777b00f036a365b38bb05e1fa6af0a507e3","tid":2276390,"uid":58120,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食一向都係自然界法則<br />\n其實食唔食肉我覺得最緊要係尊重返果個生命,<br />\n肉到你手已經係一隻死左既動物, 盡量食晒去就係最好既尊重"},{"pid":"714cf07821fea22e1c39b13cc1f0519978614a24","tid":2276390,"uid":186431,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:27:08.000Z","msg":"為什麼豬是食物，狗是竉物？"},{"pid":"74ab4b1e8fe64732efbe669a7e11766e23915b30","tid":2276390,"uid":123696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:29:14.000Z","msg":"平時唔會<br />\n<br />\n係去飲見到個豬頭或者乳鴿頭嗰陣<br />\n硬係覺得隻嘢望住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775229f57bbbcf08a8da36812b069104026452e1","tid":2276390,"uid":653,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:31:19.000Z","msg":"殺既過程睇唔到就唔會有罪惡感<br />\n君子遠刨廚"},{"pid":"525cedfefed00dffd3a8be2499e05ffa27b266b6","tid":2276390,"uid":195058,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:57:29.000Z","msg":"素撚 環保撚 道德撚"},{"pid":"8ba7c758883fe02f066e90b55f4aa8ab706d83d7","tid":2276390,"uid":125256,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"a2aea777b00f036a365b38bb05e1fa6af0a507e3","tid":2276390,"uid":58120,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食一向都係自然界法則<br />\n其實食唔食肉我覺得最緊要係尊重返果個生命,<br />\n肉到你手已經係一隻死左既動物, 盡量食晒去就係最好既尊重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"但有得揀點解唔揀食植物？<br />\n環保啲又唔駛動物受苦"},{"pid":"bbf5e165c98f53a00ee145e2291ff217b1cfed6a","tid":2276390,"uid":125256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74ab4b1e8fe64732efbe669a7e11766e23915b30","tid":2276390,"uid":123696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:29:14.000Z","msg":"平時唔會<br />\n<br />\n係去飲見到個豬頭或者乳鴿頭嗰陣<br />\n硬係覺得隻嘢望住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T21:51:14.000Z","msg":"食乳豬 蟹都會<br />\n蒸深海魚成日都覺得好醜樣 啲牙加埋對眼勁似怪物"},{"pid":"9bda13cdb3e2d681862eaaa04fad3a30aeb0b195","tid":2276390,"uid":119542,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T22:53:49.000Z","msg":"炸雞嘅屍體真係好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a009cf1e36eb4e1f0bf21eb04878dbedf0666de","tid":2276390,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:09:44.000Z","msg":"神都要羊來做祭品<br />\n<br />\n點解我唔食得肉 有得做我想做屠夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20434d6c8951284a3db96d94cacd5456518924a6","tid":2276390,"uid":85129,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:15:50.000Z","msg":"植物被殺有痛既可能，可以係真既，但豬牛羊一生會食其他肉/植物，依種被殺既痛就會重複好多次。相反食植物，大多數情況都係成世用光合作用生存，被殺既痛會比較少，食素係兩害取其輕。<br />\n<br />\n君子遠庖廚係掩耳盜鈴既做法，真君子應該要睇晒成件事。<br />\n<br />\n話順應自然個d根本戇尻，咁你何別於禽獸？人個腦就係要識諗野，抑壓獸性，先算係人<br />\n<br />\n大把素食者，高僧應該冇食supplement，呀諾都係食素，不過其實食supplement係咪好過食動物？<br />\n<br />\n根本食動物就同食貓狗冇分別，食素唔係叫大家一野戒晒肉，食少一餐得一餐，勿以善少而不為呀，第一步至少要把口認同食肉有問題先啦"},{"pid":"ac9ac401e871ad6867dc4f33a190fc9c4d09f067","tid":2276390,"uid":283741,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"你咪唔好食，少啲需求，肉類價格都冇升得咁快，我就趁平食多兩餐，多撚謝！"},{"pid":"686ccd3efe621959340a1cb6cd4f179110767779","tid":2276390,"uid":353819,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:26:16.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時諗啲人拎住碟肉影相即係拎住條屍體影<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS勿屌"},{"pid":"1ff48baf2edcf8a436ea0cab57f2974f71f6218b","tid":2276390,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:37:52.000Z","msg":"食親叉燒包都望住對面嗰個人嚟吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23c19f41a3f0126fb0fe2f4ecd3ef3421d41e4a","tid":2276390,"uid":83874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b77348060a9d19032fd3fde4307150431d0b302e","tid":2276390,"uid":96708,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:15:53.000Z","msg":"澳洲直頭合法打獵袋鼠，因為太撚多影響生態平衡，射殺完就加餸，新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:38:50.000Z","msg":"袋鼠肉幾嫩"},{"pid":"35015e972a216c46b2ad2193211e10c8297893db","tid":2276390,"uid":83874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac9ac401e871ad6867dc4f33a190fc9c4d09f067","tid":2276390,"uid":283741,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"你咪唔好食，少啲需求，肉類價格都冇升得咁快，我就趁平食多兩餐，多撚謝！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:41:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬記得炒植脂假肉，留返真肉俾我呢種窮撚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cf1a1e7c22fb0942f0ffbb9557a99b14c634d5","tid":2276390,"uid":59707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:54:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以用方法鼓勵減少食肉，但唔可以強硬叫人諗下動物幾慘，叫人食全素<br />\n你唔食肉係因為你唔想動物痛苦，但係好多人覺得人就係應該食肉<br />\n所以素肉餐單真係有得做，樓主快啲去研究多啲素肉菜譜，等多啲人習慣到有越食越多素肉先<br />\n你睇下素年開分店，周街都開始用beyond meat你就知有得做，起碼素食者同肉食者可以同檯食到大家想食嘅嘢先"},{"pid":"c971416a8920d49b48cf2611544f6b2e171fdedc","tid":2276390,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"雞豬牛羊係食素<br />\n佢地身體都係充滿植物而來既養分<br />\n而根據you are what you eat<br />\n動物都係植物既一種<br />\n<br />\n所以其實食肉=食菜"},{"pid":"9c7e3e2590df088b54fbf5aafc0bb219f1c1e1a3","tid":2276390,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"可以食少D 但係唔會唔食囉"},{"pid":"42e7fce26771d42d47cf9482f3dbc64adc1abab9","tid":2276390,"uid":79355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"冇喎 我睇唔到 我唔知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475456c39ff319016719f46c9d2e7ad249510907","tid":2276390,"uid":259565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"有時候真係會諗到 始終啲動物都有生命 <br />\n但人類為左生存同營養咁都要食嘅 <br />\n最基本我覺得係唔好浪費食物同唔好覺得應分咁囉<br />\n同埋尊重翻啲動物 俾佢地一個無咁痛苦嘅死亡 而唔係好似大陸個啲不人道方法..."},{"pid":"0d5a8da50adefd1dd3bb1eff13d397de474139b7","tid":2276390,"uid":189638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0c9642756fc2ab6bbad18e7d33f927e01211d781","tid":2276390,"uid":288455,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:21:09.000Z","msg":"人類係雜食動物，食肉係必須，你試吓食素唔食supplements 睇吓捱到幾耐？如果可以食素唔食supplements 又生存到嘅話先至好講食肉唔係必須"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"現今科技已經可以係素食產品加入大量supplements，到現時為可能未必全面停食真肉類，但過幾年科技再進步啲個講法又唔同。"},{"pid":"cb76548eeccbbecc0922b28d3f9d0a182402b567","tid":2276390,"uid":85129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"20434d6c8951284a3db96d94cacd5456518924a6","tid":2276390,"uid":85129,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:15:50.000Z","msg":"植物被殺有痛既可能，可以係真既，但豬牛羊一生會食其他肉/植物，依種被殺既痛就會重複好多次。相反食植物，大多數情況都係成世用光合作用生存，被殺既痛會比較少，食素係兩害取其輕。<br />\n<br />\n君子遠庖廚係掩耳盜鈴既做法，真君子應該要睇晒成件事。<br />\n<br />\n話順應自然個d根本戇尻，咁你何別於禽獸？人個腦就係要識諗野，抑壓獸性，先算係人<br />\n<br />\n大把素食者，高僧應該冇食supplement，呀諾都係食素，不過其實食supplement係咪好過食動物？<br />\n<br />\n根本食動物就同食貓狗冇分別，食素唔係叫大家一野戒晒肉，食少一餐得一餐，勿以善少而不為呀，第一步至少要把口認同食肉有問題先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"明人不做暗事，不服來辯"},{"pid":"4acebe3b25aba81f1ab3c3c24749349ee0b88969","tid":2276390,"uid":156121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"會 所以會盡量食哂<br />\n食動物先係自然 因為覺得殘忍而食動物 等同自殺"},{"pid":"1d800273c88c44e96a3e4f9ea91463f26b3d04e6","tid":2276390,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"食蛋會諗起雞卵巢同雞G點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3852fb9c1261fc00dfc77c567ab6f1bb25c8ef","tid":2276390,"uid":323000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"記得幾年前有研究話植物都有痛覺 又識聽音樂同聽人讚<br />\n依家次次食都諗住啲菜菜俾人掹俾人割好慘好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我同大家一樣都覺得生命係無分貴賤 就算植物都要愛惜<br />\n樓主幾時同我一樣做光合作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd09c2823790119e70c82a8c4fc60cdd10a58d25","tid":2276390,"uid":126046,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714cf07821fea22e1c39b13cc1f0519978614a24","tid":2276390,"uid":186431,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:27:08.000Z","msg":"為什麼豬是食物，狗是竉物？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"係大陸 兩樣都食得"},{"pid":"e60d7d381bef2d8bc1560a4b1920552aa704dd00","tid":2276390,"uid":193131,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d5a8da50adefd1dd3bb1eff13d397de474139b7","tid":2276390,"uid":189638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0c9642756fc2ab6bbad18e7d33f927e01211d781","tid":2276390,"uid":288455,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:21:09.000Z","msg":"人類係雜食動物，食肉係必須，你試吓食素唔食supplements 睇吓捱到幾耐？如果可以食素唔食supplements 又生存到嘅話先至好講食肉唔係必須"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"現今科技已經可以係素食產品加入大量supplements，到現時為可能未必全面停食真肉類，但過幾年科技再進步啲個講法又唔同。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做<br />\n盡量多食天然食物先係最好<br />\n食素都唔應該加多人造野落去，素肉之類不了"},{"pid":"d9f8811f9c47ac13c2c9569bdecf6b7676bed9a1","tid":2276390,"uid":58120,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ba7c758883fe02f066e90b55f4aa8ab706d83d7","tid":2276390,"uid":125256,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"a2aea777b00f036a365b38bb05e1fa6af0a507e3","tid":2276390,"uid":58120,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食一向都係自然界法則<br />\n其實食唔食肉我覺得最緊要係尊重返果個生命,<br />\n肉到你手已經係一隻